1
00:01:24,800 --> 00:01:26,260
Hu Linglong, I've said it.

2
00:01:26,640 --> 00:01:27,720
Once the words are spoken,

3
00:01:27,720 --> 00:01:28,920
they are set in stone.

4
00:01:29,280 --> 00:01:30,240
You must marry,

5
00:01:30,480 --> 00:01:31,940
whether you want to or not.

6
00:01:31,960 --> 00:01:33,200
What should we do?

7
00:01:34,840 --> 00:01:35,560
Clan Elder.

8
00:01:35,680 --> 00:01:38,410
I have previously sworn not to marry in this life.

9
00:01:38,560 --> 00:01:39,720
Forcing me now,

10
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:41,840
isn't that making me go against our ancestors?

11
00:01:41,840 --> 00:01:42,759
Humph.

12
00:01:43,360 --> 00:01:45,039
Against our ancestors?

13
00:01:45,039 --> 00:01:46,039
Hu Linglong,

14
00:01:46,039 --> 00:01:48,840
you still have the nerve to mention our ancestors?

15
00:01:48,880 --> 00:01:49,720
Back then,

16
00:01:49,960 --> 00:01:51,560
in front of our ancestors,

17
00:01:51,720 --> 00:01:53,120
how did you swear?

18
00:01:53,640 --> 00:01:55,160
Not to get involved in romance,

19
00:01:55,160 --> 00:01:57,090
not to engage in personal affairs,

20
00:01:57,320 --> 00:01:59,960
to focus solely on managing the Hu family's business,

21
00:01:59,960 --> 00:02:01,560
and never marry in your life.

22
00:02:01,560 --> 00:02:03,640
Is there a single word wrong?

23
00:02:05,760 --> 00:02:06,640
I ask you,

24
00:02:07,640 --> 00:02:09,479
do you and Xu Zhinian

25
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:12,560
have an illicit affair?

26
00:02:14,280 --> 00:02:15,760
Xu Zhinian and I are innocent.

27
00:02:15,760 --> 00:02:16,560
There is no affair.

28
00:02:16,560 --> 00:02:17,720
Nonsense.

29
00:02:18,600 --> 00:02:21,800
Half a month ago, I passed by the jewelry shop in the county town,

30
00:02:21,800 --> 00:02:23,120
and I saw you and Xu Zhinian,

31
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:24,440
the two of you,

32
00:02:24,440 --> 00:02:25,840
acting all lovey-dovey.

33
00:02:25,920 --> 00:02:27,480
You say there's nothing between you.

34
00:02:27,480 --> 00:02:28,810
Who would believe that?

35
00:02:30,840 --> 00:02:31,500
Clan Elder,

36
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:33,600
I even asked the owner of that jewelry shop.

37
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:35,360
Xu Zhinian even gave her

38
00:02:35,360 --> 00:02:37,290
a silver hairpin as a token of love.

39
00:02:38,600 --> 00:02:39,120
Clan Elder,

40
00:02:39,120 --> 00:02:41,720
this never happened.

41
00:02:41,720 --> 00:02:42,520
Hu Linglong,

42
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:44,560
Fine.

43
00:02:45,440 --> 00:02:46,440
Look at

44
00:02:46,880 --> 00:02:49,640
our Hu family's ancestors

45
00:02:50,040 --> 00:02:52,500
and swear by your father's spirit in heaven,

46
00:02:52,520 --> 00:02:54,680
that you and that boy Xu Zhinian

47
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:57,320
have absolutely no romantic feelings,

48
00:02:57,600 --> 00:02:59,200
and have a clear conscience.

49
00:02:59,720 --> 00:03:00,640
I...

50
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:02,720
Humph.

51
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:08,080
This doll,

52
00:03:08,320 --> 00:03:10,780
I sewed it secretly behind my father's back.

53
00:03:13,720 --> 00:03:15,280
I have a guilty conscience.

54
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:16,360
Long'er.

55
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:19,840
So you do.

56
00:03:20,640 --> 00:03:21,440
Hu Linglong,

57
00:03:21,880 --> 00:03:23,240
you should still remember

58
00:03:23,240 --> 00:03:25,040
when I was at the ancestral hall,

59
00:03:25,160 --> 00:03:26,360
my advice to you.

60
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:29,460
Severe punishment by the clan rules.

61
00:03:29,520 --> 00:03:30,400
Today,

62
00:03:30,960 --> 00:03:32,290
you have broken the vow.

63
00:03:32,640 --> 00:03:34,440
You are no longer free.

64
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:37,280
All your actions

65
00:03:38,079 --> 00:03:39,400
must obey

66
00:03:39,640 --> 00:03:41,240
the family's arrangements.

67
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:43,000
Hu Linglong,

68
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:45,600
don't be ungrateful.

69
00:03:45,920 --> 00:03:47,200
If you marry into the Zhang family,

70
00:03:47,200 --> 00:03:48,720
everyone will be happy.

71
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:51,840
One of the conditions of our marriage alliance

72
00:03:51,840 --> 00:03:54,079
is to help our Hu family

73
00:03:54,079 --> 00:03:55,610
open up tea sales channels.

74
00:03:55,920 --> 00:03:57,560
Since you are afraid of death

75
00:03:57,840 --> 00:04:00,520
and unwilling to go to the foreign firm to apologize,

76
00:04:00,520 --> 00:04:02,050
as the head of the family...

77
00:04:02,320 --> 00:04:03,880
You must make some sacrifices

78
00:04:03,880 --> 00:04:05,320
for the family.

79
00:04:05,720 --> 00:04:06,840
However,

80
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:08,400
once you marry into the Zhang family,

81
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:10,200
the position of the family head,

82
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:10,760
hmph,

83
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:13,520
you naturally can no longer hold it.

84
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:21,160
The son of the Zhang family is silly and foolish.

85
00:04:21,160 --> 00:04:22,420
He is over 30 years old,

86
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:24,000
has the mind of a child,

87
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:25,800
and cannot take care of himself.

88
00:04:26,200 --> 00:04:27,530
If Long'er marries him,

89
00:04:27,840 --> 00:04:29,880
it would be casting pearls before swine,

90
00:04:29,880 --> 00:04:31,800
and digging her own grave.

91
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:32,880
Clan Elder,

92
00:04:33,480 --> 00:04:36,200
please think twice.

93
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:40,680
This matter

94
00:04:41,200 --> 00:04:42,860
needs no further discussion.

95
00:04:42,880 --> 00:04:44,000
In seven days,

96
00:04:44,400 --> 00:04:45,800
it will be the wedding day

97
00:04:46,360 --> 00:04:48,420
of our Hu family and the Zhang family.

98
00:04:50,040 --> 00:04:51,159
Until then,

99
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:53,120
Hu Linglong will be

100
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:55,200
grounded at home

101
00:04:56,200 --> 00:04:58,120
and strictly guarded.

102
00:04:58,240 --> 00:04:59,360
Yes.

103
00:04:59,960 --> 00:05:00,560
Let me go.

104
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:01,280
Long'er.

105
00:05:01,280 --> 00:05:02,320
From today on,

106
00:05:02,320 --> 00:05:04,800
Hu Linglong is no longer the head of the Hu family.

107
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:05,320
Mother.

108
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:06,160
Long'er.

109
00:05:07,600 --> 00:05:08,320
Clan Elder.

110
00:05:08,640 --> 00:05:09,320
Clan Elder,

111
00:05:09,320 --> 00:05:11,050
you absolutely cannot do this.

112
00:05:11,280 --> 00:05:12,560
That young master of the Zhang family

113
00:05:12,560 --> 00:05:14,000
is a fool who needs help

114
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:15,840
with his daily life.

115
00:05:16,080 --> 00:05:17,440
How can it be so absurd

116
00:05:17,440 --> 00:05:19,370
to make Long'er condescend to him?

117
00:05:19,880 --> 00:05:20,640
Besides,

118
00:05:21,080 --> 00:05:24,080
Long'er has been the family head for less than a month.

119
00:05:26,320 --> 00:05:27,240
Clan Elder.

120
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:29,040
Li Nianci,

121
00:05:29,800 --> 00:05:32,530
how dare you still have the nerve to plead for her.

122
00:05:33,280 --> 00:05:36,040
Hu Linglong has been the family head for less than a month,

123
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:37,320
but how much trouble has she caused

124
00:05:37,320 --> 00:05:38,960
our Hu family?

125
00:05:39,560 --> 00:05:40,560
At the tea garden,

126
00:05:41,080 --> 00:05:43,000
to show off her momentary bravery,

127
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:44,760
she offended the British merchants,

128
00:05:44,760 --> 00:05:47,040
causing our Hu family's tea business

129
00:05:47,040 --> 00:05:48,720
to lose more than half.

130
00:05:48,720 --> 00:05:50,560
Do you know how much money we lost?

131
00:05:50,560 --> 00:05:51,920
As the family head,

132
00:05:52,240 --> 00:05:53,240
she handled the Japanese

133
00:05:53,240 --> 00:05:54,960
with some sense of the big picture.

134
00:05:54,960 --> 00:05:56,560
Regarding the British merchants,

135
00:05:56,560 --> 00:05:58,360
I also defended her a lot.

136
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:00,280
But she,

137
00:06:01,080 --> 00:06:02,000
she dared to

138
00:06:02,440 --> 00:06:03,400
break the oath

139
00:06:03,400 --> 00:06:04,760
she made in front of

140
00:06:04,760 --> 00:06:06,120
our ancestors,

141
00:06:07,640 --> 00:06:09,240
and was intimately involved

142
00:06:09,480 --> 00:06:11,400
with that boy named Xu Zhinian.

143
00:06:11,760 --> 00:06:13,520
Having an affair,

144
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:15,760
how shameless!

145
00:06:16,520 --> 00:06:17,080
Ptooi!

146
00:06:17,680 --> 00:06:18,540
Listen to that.

147
00:06:20,680 --> 00:06:21,600
How could this be?

148
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:23,130
What kind of mother are you?

149
00:06:23,720 --> 00:06:24,160
Clan Elder,

150
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:24,800
calm down

151
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:25,800
and have some tea.

152
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:29,560
Li Nianci.

153
00:06:30,640 --> 00:06:31,520
Hu Linglong

154
00:06:31,520 --> 00:06:33,040
must take responsibility

155
00:06:33,880 --> 00:06:35,680
for the great mistakes she made.

156
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:37,400
Either

157
00:06:37,920 --> 00:06:39,760
go to the English Bank

158
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:41,770
to confess and commit suicide,

159
00:06:41,840 --> 00:06:42,520
or

160
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:44,800
you obediently listen to me

161
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:46,920
and marry into the Zhang family.

162
00:06:48,400 --> 00:06:49,840
There are only two paths

163
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:51,320
before you.

164
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:53,400
Will she choose herself,

165
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:55,760
or will you choose for her?

166
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:07,360
Hu Linglong has made

167
00:07:07,640 --> 00:07:09,000
more than one mistake.

168
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:10,120
Today,

169
00:07:10,400 --> 00:07:11,800
she has more than one path

170
00:07:11,840 --> 00:07:13,040
given to her.

171
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:15,280
Tell Hu Linglong

172
00:07:16,000 --> 00:07:17,200
not to be ungrateful.

173
00:07:18,360 --> 00:07:18,760
Humph.

174
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:21,960
Aunt Li,

175
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:23,820
think about it carefully.

176
00:07:38,920 --> 00:07:39,800
[Cough]

177
00:07:47,800 --> 00:07:49,800
The Hu family has already come to me.

178
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:51,880
From now on, you are not allowed to have

179
00:07:51,880 --> 00:07:53,560
any contact with Hu Linglong.

180
00:07:55,360 --> 00:07:57,920
She is now the future daughter-in-law of the Zhang family.

181
00:07:57,920 --> 00:07:58,980
Do you understand?

182
00:08:00,360 --> 00:08:00,760
But...

183
00:08:00,800 --> 00:08:01,640
No buts.

184
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:03,720
The most important thing for you now is

185
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:05,120
to get fully prepared

186
00:08:05,120 --> 00:08:07,450
and take up your post in the Beiyang Fleet.

187
00:08:07,720 --> 00:08:09,440
A real man's ambition is everywhere.

188
00:08:09,440 --> 00:08:11,200
How can you be trapped by romantic feelings?

189
00:08:11,200 --> 00:08:13,040
How did I teach you before?

190
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:19,580
Before Hu Linglong marries young master Zhang,

191
00:08:19,800 --> 00:08:22,200
you are not allowed to step out of the house.

192
00:08:22,520 --> 00:08:23,780
If you dare to disobey,

193
00:08:23,840 --> 00:08:25,500
I will not let you off lightly.

194
00:08:31,400 --> 00:08:31,760
Sigh.

195
00:08:31,760 --> 00:08:32,360
Elders.

196
00:08:32,480 --> 00:08:33,480
I mean,

197
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:34,720
this family

198
00:08:34,880 --> 00:08:36,039
cannot be without a master for a single day.

199
00:08:36,039 --> 00:08:36,799
Yes.

200
00:08:36,799 --> 00:08:37,200
Right.

201
00:08:37,440 --> 00:08:37,799
Yeah.

202
00:08:38,520 --> 00:08:40,580
This is a matter of great importance.

203
00:08:41,679 --> 00:08:42,640
We will discuss it another day.

204
00:08:42,640 --> 00:08:43,039
Hey,

205
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:43,760
elders.

206
00:08:43,919 --> 00:08:44,280
Hey,

207
00:08:44,280 --> 00:08:44,880
elders.

208
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:48,680
That old geezer.

209
00:08:51,240 --> 00:08:51,720
Tsk.

210
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:52,730
Let's go.

211
00:08:57,880 --> 00:08:58,760
What?

212
00:08:59,280 --> 00:09:01,080
While I was asleep in the jade pendant,

213
00:09:01,080 --> 00:09:02,800
they actually asked you to marry a fool,

214
00:09:02,800 --> 00:09:04,200
and you actually agreed.

215
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:06,560
If I had been there,

216
00:09:06,720 --> 00:09:09,440
I would definitely have helped you vent your anger.

217
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:12,100
From the moment I stepped into the council hall,

218
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:13,970
this was their conspiracy.

219
00:09:14,160 --> 00:09:16,120
No matter which of us faces it,

220
00:09:16,520 --> 00:09:18,450
the ending won't be any different.

221
00:09:19,760 --> 00:09:20,520
But

222
00:09:20,640 --> 00:09:21,880
your constant forbearance

223
00:09:21,880 --> 00:09:23,480
will only make them go from bad to worse.

224
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:24,320
What happened today

225
00:09:24,320 --> 00:09:25,640
is the best proof.

226
00:09:25,720 --> 00:09:27,180
Don't you understand yet?

227
00:09:27,720 --> 00:09:28,680
I understand.

228
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:32,620
But I don't want to involve anyone else anymore.

229
00:09:32,880 --> 00:09:33,560
My mother,

230
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:35,240
Zhinian,

231
00:09:35,800 --> 00:09:36,880
and Uncle Zhao.

232
00:09:37,960 --> 00:09:40,400
I know these are all Hu Wenyi's tricks.

233
00:09:41,400 --> 00:09:42,440
But no matter what,

234
00:09:42,440 --> 00:09:45,300
I won't marry that young master of the Zhang family.

235
00:09:45,400 --> 00:09:46,930
What you just said is right.

236
00:09:47,840 --> 00:09:49,600
So even if it costs my life,

237
00:09:49,640 --> 00:09:51,570
I will make them pay for their sins.

238
00:09:52,520 --> 00:09:54,160
What do you mean by that?

239
00:09:54,640 --> 00:09:56,920
You are not going to throw your life away, are you?

240
00:09:56,920 --> 00:09:58,360
Think about what will happen to your mother,

241
00:09:58,360 --> 00:09:59,320
the Hu family,

242
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:01,880
and the improved black tea.

243
00:10:03,080 --> 00:10:05,810
Some wishes are destined to remain unfulfilled.

244
00:10:06,240 --> 00:10:09,240
Maybe that's why they are called long-cherished wishes.

245
00:10:09,240 --> 00:10:10,200
Hu Linglong.

246
00:10:10,200 --> 00:10:11,600
How can you be so foolish?

247
00:10:32,680 --> 00:10:33,680
I'll do it myself.

248
00:10:41,680 --> 00:10:42,680
I just treat this as

249
00:10:42,680 --> 00:10:44,880
a thank-you gift for keeping my secret.

250
00:10:44,920 --> 00:10:46,250
Forget it, give it back.

251
00:10:46,680 --> 00:10:47,360
Since you gave it to me,

252
00:10:47,360 --> 00:10:48,620
you can't take it back.

253
00:10:49,720 --> 00:10:51,080
This is the Hu family's tea factory.

254
00:10:51,080 --> 00:10:52,360
Let's see who dares to make a move.

255
00:10:52,360 --> 00:10:53,520
Linglong.

256
00:10:58,000 --> 00:10:58,720
Come up.
